
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Booking Updated</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { background-color: #FFC107; color: #111; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .notes-content { white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Booking Updated</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>Your booking has been updated successfully. Here are the latest details:</p>
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{bookingId}}</p>
                <p><strong>Service:</strong> {{service}}</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>
                <p><strong>Notes:</strong> <span class="notes-content">{{{notes}}}</span></p>
            </div>
            <p>If this update was not made by you, please contact us immediately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Booking System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
